thread.title: José Colaço
thread.title_full: Autoclick Rent a Car evaluado por José Colaço

author: José Colaço
title: José Colaço
text:
I've been overcharged by mistake.
The customer service is practically nonexistent and they communicate only in English for Portuguese customers.
They make digital copies of personal documents without customer permission.
If you buy something from this guys over the internet, stick with that and don't ask for anything at the office !
